      <block class="full_text">
        <p>JOHN MADDEN, the movie star? Now that Madden is the top football analyst for Fox Sports, anything is possible. Yesterday, he began filming a role as himself in a comedy, "Little Giants," about Little League football.</p>
        <p>In the movie, the former CBS announcer's "All-Madden Bus," filled with players like EMMITT SMITH, BRUCE SMITH and STEVE EMTMAN, breaks down. The stars play with the kids and Madden gives plays to the coach of the least adept team. "We leave and the kids win," Madden said. "This will be my first, last and only movie."  SPORTS PEOPLE: FOOTBALL</p>
      </block>
